## Checklist

### Content Quality

- [ ] Follows the [Style Guide](STYLE_GUIDE.md)
- [ ] Uses non-stigmatizing, person-first language
- [ ] Includes appropriate cross-references to related content
- [ ] Uses GitHub Alerts (`[!NOTE]`, `[!TIP]`, etc.) where appropriate

### Ethical Compliance

- [ ] All dorks search for **publicly available** information only
- [ ] No queries target personal or identifiable information
- [ ] Content supports **legitimate harm reduction purposes**
- [ ] Aligns with the [Code of Conduct](CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md) and [Security Guidelines](SECURITY.md)

### Technical

- [ ] No broken links introduced
- [ ] Code blocks use `txt` language hint for dorks
- [ ] Live search links are properly URL-encoded (where included)
